{"tid":1046955,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[怨婦] 高普成英超籍口王","createTime":"2019-03-04T15:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T15:49:29.000Z","uid":209679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bff8c1682fd30cf745583c4d7d087e7769bba9b","tid":1046955,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4N3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=4b189139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦在默西塞德打吡與愛華頓賽和0:0，失去英超榜首之位，領隊高普再為失分找藉口，成為英超藉口王。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦領隊高普（Jurgen Klopp）領軍與愛華頓於打吡戰悶和0:0之後，表示失利與球場太大風有關係；原來，這位德國籍領隊已經不是第1次埋怨天氣。<br />\n<br />\n早於2015年，高普剛接手紅軍領隊一職時，球隊開季只排第10，他接受訪問時透露，自己面對完全不同風格的足球，更指表現欠佳的部份原因，是英國的風太大，非英國球員要花更多時間適應。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年1月，利物浦在聯賽盃4強敗陣於修咸頓的腳下，高普再次在賽後表示球場太大風，影響了球員的判斷及紅軍的發揮。<br />\n<br />\n及至2018年初，紅軍於足總盃不敵西布朗，高普賽後指摘球證補時不足：「我聽聞補時應該有10分鐘，但只得4分鐘。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怨婦猁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253e0fbc98495df040766c1e0c837ea0b368a112","tid":1046955,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"Respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a86a26c63fcc254dbc689578e14789be3d0500","tid":1046955,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/233428_f416b7a4df41a97012358756c2a46d29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F233428_f416b7a4df41a97012358756c2a46d29.png&h=78933de8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"837d6f117a7d8d9217de423d09631736b65d82ce","tid":1046955,"uid":3194,